name: COMPULSIVE // SUN OF FUTURE
description:
Victory shines so brightly, so brightly it can blind peoples eyes.
Nothing could be seen around him, only a bright spot of light in front of him.
Waiting for the results of winning or losing brings the sensation of feeling tense into an addiction.
Without them knowing the bright spot they are shining for is a false victory.
Absolute victory in fact has a place opposite from where they are headed.
